### GPT Streaming Request - Chat Completions
### Expected: SSE stream with chat completion chunks

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Explain quantum computing in 2 sentences"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true,
  "max_tokens": 100
}

### GPT Non-Streaming Request - Chat Completions
### Expected: JSON response with complete completion

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What is the capital of France?"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 50
}

### Kimi Request - Chat Completions via Azure AI Foundry
### Expected: JSON completion response

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "kimi",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello, how are you?"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 50
}

### Claude Rejection - Wrong Protocol
### Expected: 400 error - Claude models only available via /v1/messages
### Claude is routed to anthropic-messages protocol, not chat-completions

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hello Claude"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 50
}

### max_tokens Deprecation Warning Scenario
### Expected: Request should still work but max_tokens may be deprecated
### Some API versions return warnings for max_tokens usage

POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Give me a list of 3 colors"
    }
  ],
  "stream": false,
  "max_tokens": 30
}
